Package: lecture-08
Title: SOC 4650/5650 - Lecture 08 - Demographic Data
Version: 18.3.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Prener", email = "chris.prener@slu.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is the repository for Lecture 08 of the Saint Louis University 
    course SOC 4650/5650 - Introduction to GIS. This lecture covers tools for
    accessing demographic and gemetric data both from the web and using R. The
    R packages tidycensus and tigris are introduced.
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
